affected(string).notice: affected - Returns all output files affected by a change to a source file.

audit(string).notice: audit - Audits all files in an output directory for drift from their stored content hashes.

clean(string,string[]).notice: clean - Removes files not in the current manifest from the output directory.

format(string).notice: format - Formats an emitted file according to its format hint.

manifest(string).notice: manifest - Lists all tracked files in an output directory.

trace(string).notice: trace - Returns the source provenance for an emitted file.

write(string,string,string,bytes[]).notice: write - Content-addressed file write with deduplication.

writeBatch(bytes[]).notice: writeBatch - Writes multiple files in a single transaction.
